name: SIDAKARYA MASK
description:
The name of Sidakarya Mask Dance comes from two words, namely mask and Sidakarya.

Topeng comes from the word tup which means to close. Sidakarya comes from the word sida which means to achieve, and work which means goal or work.

So, Sidakarya itself has the meaning of achieving a goal or completing a job.

The Sidakarya mask is also a symbol that the work or work that was held has been completed properly.
